   5) have snare up that last mob is gonna run once all the others are dead and with the armory the last mobs tend to be the ore cart lizzies or the armory overseer if he is up  this may help you it may not but at lvl 56 i get about 15% aa exp per pull and 4% reg exp and make a couple kp each night from gem drops and such, also have used this technique to allow guild and friend alts to join me in my kites while they single pull the wharehouses to the short wall in courtyard i kite the rest all get some fast easy exp cause with a 18 mod brass and triple twisting the songs it takes about 10-15minutes to do(bit more if you have to regen back 2-3khps)<br><br>ps ive ae kited from lvl 23-56.. lol now time to learn how to swarm/charm kite since ae kite spots getting hard to find<br><br><i><span class="sm">Edited, Tue Jun 29 23:01:47 2004 by QueII</span class="sm"></i></p><br /><span class="sm">----------------------------</span><br />Bearfooted Bugsmoosher(primary account)<br>Beastlord(ogre) 65th season<br>Tholuxe Paells server<br>guardians of valour<br><br>Bagmaker <br>Druid(halfling) 52nd season<br>guardians of valour<br><br>Swiftfeett killertunes(secondary account)<br>Bard(wood elf)65th season<br>guardians of valour</td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform2"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8"></td><td align="right" id="fs8" >0 Replies</td></tr></table>
